  "text": "Membrane cleaning can effectively remove and control membrane fouling, reduce TMP, and restore membrane flux [CITATION_1] . The cleaning methods of contaminants in the MBR process can be divided into physical cleaning, chemical cleaning, and electric cleaning. In the actual operation process, it is difficult to achieve the best results with a single cleaning method. Generally, a combination of several methods will be effective in cleaning the membrane [CITATION_2] .",
